tplinkDhcpSnoopingMIB.name: tplinkDhcpSnoopingMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

tplinkDhcpSnoopingMIB.description: Private MIB for DHCP Snooping configuration.

dhcpSnoopingEnable.name: dhcpSnoopingEnable
dhcpSnoopingEnable.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable or disable the DHCP Snooping function globally.

dhcpSnoopingVlanConfigTable.name: dhcpSnoopingVlanConfigTable
dhcpSnoopingVlanConfigTable.description: Here you can view and modify the DHCP Snooping VLAN config table.

dhcpSnoopingVlanConfigEntry.name: dhcpSnoopingVlanConfigEntry
dhcpSnoopingVlanConfigEntry.description: An entry contains of the DHCP Snooping function enable status information of a VLAN.

dhcpSnoopingVlanId.name: dhcpSnoopingVlanId
dhcpSnoopingVlanId.description: Enter the ID number of VLAN,1-4094.

dhcpSnoopingVlanStatus.name: dhcpSnoopingVlanStatus
dhcpSnoopingVlanStatus.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable or disable DHCP Snooping function in specified VLAN.

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigTable.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigTable
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigTable.description: A list of DHCP Snooping option 82 config entries. Here you can configure the port parameters for the DHCP Snooping option 82 feature.

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigEntry.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigEntry
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigEntry.description: An entry contains of the information of dhcp snooping option 82 config.

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigSupportStatus.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigSupportStatus
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigSupportStatus.description: 0. disable 1. enable Select Enable/Disable the port to support the Option 82 feature.

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigOperationStrat.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigOperationStrategy
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigOperationStrat.description: Select the operation for the Option 82 filed of the DHCP request packets from the Host. 0. keep: Indicates to keep the Option 82 field of the packets. 1. replace: Indicates to replace the Option 82 field of the packets with the switch defined one. 2. drop: Indicates to discard the packets including the Option 82 field.

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigCircuitCustomi.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigCircuitCustomization
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigCircuitCustomi.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable/Disable the switch to define the Option 82 circuit id.

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigCircuitID.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigCircuitID
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigCircuitID.description: The sub-option Circuit ID for the customized Option 82.(1-64 characters)

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigRemoteCustomiz.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigRemoteCustomization
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigRemoteCustomiz.description: 0. disable 1. enable Enable/Disable the switch to define the Option 82 remote id.

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigRemoteID.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigRemoteID
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigRemoteID.description: The sub-option Remote ID for the customized Option 82.(1-64 characters)

dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigLag.name: dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigLag
dhcpSnoopingOption82ConfigLag.description: The LAG to which the port belongs to.

dhcpSnoopingPortConfigTable.name: dhcpSnoopingPortConfigTable
dhcpSnoopingPortConfigTable.description: A list of DHCP Snooping port config entries. Here you can configure the port parameters for the DHCP Snooping.

dhcpSnoopingPortConfigEntry.name: dhcpSnoopingPortConfigEntry
dhcpSnoopingPortConfigEntry.description: An entry contains of the information of DHCP Snooping port config.

dhcpSnoopingPortConfigTrustedPort.name: dhcpSnoopingPortConfigTrustedPort
dhcpSnoopingPortConfigTrustedPort.description: 0. disable 1. enable Select Enable/Disable the port to be a Trusted Port. Only the Trusted Port can receive the DHCP packets from DHCP servers.

dhcpSnoopingPortConfigMacVerify.name: dhcpSnoopingPortConfigMacVerify
dhcpSnoopingPortConfigMacVerify.description: 0. disable 1. enable Select Enable/Disable the MAC Verify feature. There are two fields of the DHCP packet containing the MAC address of the Host. The MAC Verify feature is to compare the two fields and discard the packet if the two fields are different.

dhcpSnoopingPortConfigRateLimit.name: dhcpSnoopingPortConfigRateLimit
dhcpSnoopingPortConfigRateLimit.description: 0. disable 1. 5pps 2. 10pps 3. 15pps 4. 20pps 5. 25pps 6. 30pps Select Enable/Disable the Flow Control feature for the DHCP packets. The excessive DHCP packets will be discarded.

dhcpSnoopingPortConfigDeclineRateLimit.name: dhcpSnoopingPortConfigDeclineRateLimit
dhcpSnoopingPortConfigDeclineRateLimit.description: 0. disable 1. 5pps 2. 10pps 3. 15pps 4. 20pps 5. 25pps 6. 30pps Select Enable/Disable the Flow Control feature for the DHCP decline packets. The excessive DHCP decline packets will be discarded.

dhcpSnoopingPortConfigPortLag.name: dhcpSnoopingPortConfigPortLag
dhcpSnoopingPortConfigPortLag.description: The LAG to which the port belongs to.
